text.tspan: And those who were with me beheld the light,
But did not hear the voice of the One,
And I said, What shall I do, Lord?
And the Lord said, Rise up and go,
And the Lord said, Rise up and go,
Go into Damascus, there it will be told to you
Concerning all the things appointed you.
And a certain man then came to me, saying,
And in that very hour, I looked up at him
And he said, our God already appointed you
To know His will and to see the righteous One,
To know His will and to see the righteous One
And to hear His voice; For you will be a witness
Unto all men of the things youve seen and heard.
And now, why do you delay?
And wash away your sins, calling on His name.
Wash away your sins, calling on His name!
And I answered, Who are You, Lord?
And I answered, Who are You, Lord?
And He said to me, I am Jesus,
Jesus the Nazarene, whom you believe.
